- Technical Details
    - Tech Stack:
        - HTML, React 18 (CDN UMD), in-browser Babel Standalone
        - site_kit (https://k1monfared.github.io/site_kit/) for chrome
        - Node 20 for dev tooling: ajv + ajv-formats, @playwright/test, http-server
        - GitHub Actions for CI
    - Key Files:
        - index.html: app shell (React + Babel loaders)
        - app.jsx: single-file SPA; Browse, Detail, Text, Compare components
        - licenses.css: page-specific styles (theme variables come from site_kit)
        - schemas/: meta, features, analysis, progress, index, feature-vocabulary
        - licenses/index.json: browse catalog
        - licenses/<id>/: meta.json, text.raw.txt, text.html, features.json, analysis.json (optional), .progress.json
        - scripts/validate.mjs: schema + citation liveness + sha256 provenance + source-completeness
        - scripts/tokenizer.mjs: deterministic idempotent sentence splitter with s-N ids
        - scripts/router.mjs: hash-route parser
        - .claude/skills/: lookup-license, extract-features, deep-analysis
        - .claude/commands/: add-license, backfill-feature, refresh-analysis
        - .github/workflows/validate.yml: CI test + validate on push/PR
        - tests/smoke.spec.mjs: playwright smoke (browse, detail, compare, text-highlight)

